snippet.title: SYNTHROME - Dissonance Teaser (July Update)
snippet.description:
🌿 Dissonance: Forest of Echoes 🌿

Enter the remnants of a once-lush forest, now twisted by the SYNs' corruption. In "Dissonance," choose your path: speed through the haunting landscape or navigate intricate jumping platforms. Uncover hidden secrets and avoid dangerous hazards as you pursue the elusive Sphere of Hope.

🏞️ Lush but Treacherous - Traverse a forest where beauty and danger coexist. The path you take will determine your journey's outcome.

⚡ Multiple Paths, One Goal - Speedrun through the dangers or take a slower, more strategic route. The choice is yours.
KEEP AN EYE OUT👁️
#Synthrome #videogames #indiegame #unrealengine5 #ue5
